  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/4112d8ba08bad0b2fc24a438ff6083f8.poster.avif?t=1734896472\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/4112d8ba08bad0b2fc24a438ff6083f8.webm?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/4112d8ba08bad0b2fc24a438ff6083f8.mp4?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>FEATURES:</strong></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill based  combat + Base defense</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tons of upgrades: Weapons, Walls, Turrets, Coin farms, Builders, Turrets, etc.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CO-OP on a single keyboard or controllers</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ unique enemies</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hours of original music</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/cbbafdf10f49763a2292474e11ec5353.poster.avif?t=1734896472\" width=540 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/cbbafdf10f49763a2292474e11ec5353.webm?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/cbbafdf10f49763a2292474e11ec5353.mp4?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build walls, shields, and turrets, or take the fight into your own hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Greediness system allows minimalist builds to be viable, and rewarding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock advanced items to upgrade your movement, weapons, economy, and base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Return to previous worlds with new items to destroy unbeaten hoards and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/6a1d9fe424c96f7c26fa98238dffff6a.poster.avif?t=1734896472\" width=540 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/6a1d9fe424c96f7c26fa98238dffff6a.webm?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/6a1d9fe424c96f7c26fa98238dffff6a.mp4?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/4112d8ba08bad0b2fc24a438ff6083f8.poster.avif?t=1734896472\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/4112d8ba08bad0b2fc24a438ff6083f8.webm?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/4112d8ba08bad0b2fc24a438ff6083f8.mp4?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>FEATURES:</strong></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skill based  combat + Base defense</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tons of upgrades: Weapons, Walls, Turrets, Coin farms, Builders, Turrets, etc.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CO-OP on a single keyboard or controllers</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ unique enemies</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hours of original music</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/cbbafdf10f49763a2292474e11ec5353.poster.avif?t=1734896472\" width=540 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/cbbafdf10f49763a2292474e11ec5353.webm?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/cbbafdf10f49763a2292474e11ec5353.mp4?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build walls, shields, and turrets, or take the fight into your own hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Greediness system allows minimalist builds to be viable, and rewarding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock advanced items to upgrade your movement, weapons, economy, and base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Return to previous worlds with new items to destroy unbeaten hoards and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/6a1d9fe424c96f7c26fa98238dffff6a.poster.avif?t=1734896472\" width=540 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/6a1d9fe424c96f7c26fa98238dffff6a.webm?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324100/extras/6a1d9fe424c96f7c26fa98238dffff6a.mp4?t=1734896472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
